<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"> 0 &le; C, |S| &le; 1000</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><strong>Constraints - 60% </strong></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"> 1 &le; T &le; 100</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"> 0 &le; C, |S| &le; 1000000&nbsp;</p></span></span></span></pre>

